_________________________________________________________________________________________________
WHAT:

This C++ code is written using Deal II library for printing out mass and stiffness matrices for
Discontinuous Galerkin (DG) elements in tensor-product spaces.

Features:
1. Arbitrary order reconstruction
2. Exact or inexact integration
3. 1D, 2D or 3D grids


_________________________________________________________________________________________________
WHY:

This code was written to generate mass and stiffness matrix for validation of in-house code on
arbitrary order grids in multi-dim. The matrices generated can be used for comparing those 
by the in-house code, in a way as a validation tool. This is important since such validation is 
not easily available for coders.
_________________________________________________________________________________________________
OTHER RESOURCES:

1. DealII tutorial programs (https://www.dealii.org/8.4.0/doxygen/deal.II/Tutorial.html)
2. CFD codes given on Dr. Praveen Chandrashekar's website (http://cpraveen.github.io/codes.html)
3. Video lectures of Dr. Wolfgang Bangerth (http://www.math.colostate.edu/~bangerth/videos.html)

_________________________________________________________________________________________________
TO RUN:
_________________________________________________________________________________________________
No.       command	 	Action                    Effect 			       
_________________________________________________________________________________________________
1.                           install deal.ii              you get DealII !                            
2.    cmake .                press enter                  extract                                
      (note, you may have to pass the path, i.e.   cmake -DDEAL_II_DIR=pathToDealII .
       where, pathToDealII is the path to your deal II folder)
3.    make 		     press enter                  compile 		               
4.    ./DGMat		     press enter                  run  			       
5.    make distclean         press enter                  clean the folder                          
_________________________________________________________________________________________________
